.oxm.co.uk/46662/minecraft-xbox-360-update-182-out-today-10am-gmt/|archive-date=2012-10-19|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.oxm.co.uk/46307/minecraft-xbox-360-update-182-4j-releases-enormous-final-contents-list/|title=Minecraft Xbox 360 update 1.8.2 - 4J releases enormous final contents list|work=[[官方Xbox杂志|Official Xbox Magazine]]|publisher=[[Future_plc|Future plc]]|first=Edwin|last=Evans-Thirlwell|date=2012-10-02|accessdate=2012-10-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121107103008/http://www.oxm.co.uk/46307/minecraft-xbox-360-update-182-4j-releases-enormous-final-contents-list/|archive-date=2012-11-07|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2013年[[Gamescom|科隆国际游戏展]]上，[[索尼|索尼]]宣布《我的世界》将在PlayStation 4平台首发，随后登陆[[PlayStation_Vita|PlayStation Vita]]和[[PlayStation_3|PlayStation 3]]平台<ref name="ps4_launch">{{cite web |url=http://uk.ign.com/articles/2013/08/20/gamescom-minecraft-coming-to-ps4 |title=Gamescom: Minecraft Coming to PS4, PS3, Vita – IGN |publisher=Uk.ign.com |date=2013-08-20 |accessdate=2013-12-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141121072700/http://uk.ign.com/articles/2013/08/20/gamescom-minecraft-coming-to-ps4 |archive-date=2014-11-21 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。但游戏后来跳票<ref name="gamespot1">{{cite web |url=http://www.gamespot.com/articles/minecraft-not-launching-with-playstation-4/1100-6416102/ |title=Minecraft not launching with PS4 |publisher=GameSpot |date=2013-11-12 |accessdate=2013-11-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131114094958/http://www.gamespot.com/articles/minecraft-not-launching-with-playstation-4/1100-6416102/ |archive-date=2013-11-14 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2013年12月17日，《我的世界》在PlayStation 3平台推出。2014年9月4日在PlayStation 4推出<ref>{{cite web|last1=Pitcher|first1=Jenna|title=Minecraft PS4 Edition Release Date Confirmed|url=http://www.ign.com/articles/2014/09/04/minecraft-ps4-edition-release-date-confirmed|website=IGN|publisher=IGN Entertainment, Inc.|accessdate=2014-10-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141001124534/http://www.ign.com/articles/2014/09/04/minecraft-ps4-edition-release-date-confirmed|archive-date=2014-10-01|dead-url=no}}</ref>，10月14日PlayStation Vita版在北美推出，次日在欧洲推出<ref name="vita_launch">{{cite web | url=http://uk.ign.com/articles/2014/10/10/minecraft-ps-vita-edition-release-date-revealed-for-north-america | title=Minecraft: PS Vita Edition Release Date Revealed for North America | work=IGN | first=Evan | last=Campbell | date=2014-10-10 | accessdate=2015-02-15 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151106170435/http://uk.ign.com/articles/2014/10/10/minecraft-ps-vita-edition-release-date-revealed-for-north-america | archive-date=2015-11-06 | dead-url=no }}</ref>。与Xbox版本一样，PlayStation版本同样由4J Studios开发，功能与Xbox 360版几乎相同<ref>{{cite web |url=http://minecraft.gamepedia.com/PlayStation_3_Edition |title=Minecraft Wiki: PlayStation 3 Edition |date=2014-01-16 |accessdate=2014-01-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140126162030/http://minecraft.gamepedia.com/Playstation_3_Edition |archive-date=2014-01-26 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

在{{le|E3 2013|E3 2013}}新闻发布会上，微软公布了《我的世界》的[[Xbox_One|Xbox One]]版<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.ign.com/articles/2013/06/10/e3-2013-minecraft-coming-to-xbox-one |title=E3 2013: Minecraft Coming to Xbox One |publisher=IGN |date=2013-06-10 |accessdate=2013-06-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130613033834/http://www.ign.com/articles/2013/06/10/e3-2013-minecraft-coming-to-xbox-one |archive-date=2013-06-13 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。此版本与Xbox 360版类似，但拥有更大的世界，拓展了多人游戏功能以及增强了其他功能。Xbox One版发布于2014年9月5日<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=unVcuWYW0GI |title=Minecraft: Xbox One Edition Announce Trailer |publisher=Microsoft |date=2013-06-10 |accessdate=2013-06-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130617214819/http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=unVcuWYW0GI |archive-date=2013-06-17 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2015年8月，Xbox中国宣布引进Xbox One版<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.weibo.com/5203472552/CwRJ8rEbz |title=欢迎来到《我的世界》 |author=Xbox |work=新浪微博 |date=2015-08-21 |access-date=2015-08-27 |archive-date=2022-05-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220504221513/https://www.weibo.com/5203472552/CwRJ8rEbz }}</ref>。9月29日，《Minecraft：Xbox One》国行版发布。

