诸如[[YouTube|YouTube]]、[[Facebook|Facebook]]和[[Reddit|Reddit]]等社交媒体网站在《我的世界》普及过程中起到了重要作用<ref name="Social media">{{cite web | url=http://mashable.com/2010/10/01/minecraft-social-media/ | title=Minecraft: How Social Media Spawned a Gaming Sensation | work=[[Mashable|Mashable]] | publisher=Mashable Inc. | date=2010-10-01 | accessdate=2012-12-28 | last=Silverman | first=Matt | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121230080505/http://mashable.com/2010/10/01/minecraft-social-media/ | archive-date=2012-12-30 | dead-url=no }}</ref>。[[宾夕法尼亚大学|宾夕法尼亚大学]]安纳伯格传播学院进行的一项研究显示，三分之一的《我的世界》玩家通过互联网视频了解这款游戏<ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.gamespot.com/news/mining-data-from-minecraft-6331569 | title=Mining data from Minecraft | publisher=[[CBS互動|CBS Interactive]] | work=[[GameSpot|GameSpot]] | date=2011-08-28 | accessdate=2012-12-28 | last=Tong | first=Sophia | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130308095214/http://www.gamespot.com/news/mining-data-from-minecraft-6331569 | archive-date=2013-03-08 | dead-url=no }}</ref>。2010年，《我的世界》相关视频开始在YouTube盈利。这些视频多由评论员制作，通常包含游戏的屏幕捕获镜头和旁白<ref name="salon">{{cite web |title=Inside the geeky, revolutionary world of "Minecraft" |url=http://www.salon.com/2011/12/06/inside_the_geeky_revolutionary_world_of_minecraft/singleton/ |work=Salon |publisher=Salon Media Group |first=Rob |last=Spillman |date=2011-12-06 |accessdate=2013-11-23 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130117145332/http://www.salon.com/2011/12/06/inside_the_geeky_revolutionary_world_of_minecraft/singleton/ |archivedate=2013-01-17 }}</ref>。视频中常见的内容包括玩家展示其制作的作品、各种[[攻略本|游戏攻略]]和对流行作品的模仿。截至2012年5月，超过400万《我的世界》相关视频在YouTube被上传<ref name="Merchandise sales" />。一些知名评论员收到了游戏视频公司{{le|Machinima (游戏公司)|Machinima Inc.|Machinima}}的聘请，该公司在YouTube拥有一个人气很高的娱乐频道<ref name="salon" />。{{le|The Yogscast|The Yogscast}}是英国一个定期制作《我的世界》视频的组织，他们的小组在2011年的[[MineCon|MineCon]]中有着很高的出席率<ref name="salon" /><ref name="bbc tycoons">{{cite web|title=The TV tycoons you may have missed|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/technology-18768443|work=[[英國廣播公司新聞網|BBC News Online]]|publisher=BBC|accessdate=2012-07-10|first=Rory|last=Cellan-Jones|date=2012-07-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120805071240/http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/technology-18768443|archive-date=2012-08-05|dead-url=no}}</ref>。其他知名的YouTube主播有[[乔丹·马伦|乔丹·马伦]]（Jordan Maron），他制作了许多的Minecraft的[[戲仿|戲仿]]视频，包括对韩国说唱歌手[[PSY|PSY]]的知名单曲《[[江南Style|江南Style]]》的[[戲仿|戲仿]]视频“Minecraft Style”<ref name="Minecraft Style">{{cite web | url=http://sys03-public.nbcnews.com/technology/dig-minecraft-style-gangnam-style-parody-1C6601764 | title=Dig this 'Minecraft'-style 'Gangnam Style' parody | work=[[NBC新聞|NBC News]] | publisher=[[NBC環球|NBCUniversal]] | date=2012-10-23 | accessdate=2012-12-09 | last=Benedetti | first=Winda | deadurl=yes | archiveurl=https://archive.is/20140610202513/http://sys03-public.nbcnews.com/technology/dig-minecraft-style-gangnam-style-parody-1C6601764 | archivedate=2014-06-10 }}</ref>。[[籽岷|籽岷]]是中国大陆最知名的《我的世界》主播之一<ref>{{Cite web|url = http://www.962.net/gl/135997.html|title = 我的世界籽岷是谁|accessdate = 2016-02-22|author = |date = 2015-07-08|publisher = 乐游网|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160303222110/http://www.962.net/gl/135997.html|archive-date = 2016-03-03|dead-url = no}}</ref>，他的[[优酷网|优酷]]自频道的视频播放数超过6亿<ref>{{Cite web|url = http://i.youku.com/i/UNTU1Mzg3Mzk2|title = 籽岷的自频道-优酷视频|accessdate = 2021-05-22|author = |date = {{FULLDATE|type=date}}|publisher = 优酷网|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201128002911/http://i.youku.com/i/UNTU1Mzg3Mzk2|archive-date = 2020-11-28|dead-url = no}}</ref>，[[Bilibili|Bilibili]]播放数超过5.5亿<ref>{{Cite web|url = https://space.bilibili.com/686127|title = 籽岷的个人空间 - 哔哩哔哩 ( ゜- ゜)つロ 乾杯~ Bilibili|accessdate = 2021-05-22|author = |date = {{FULLDATE|type=date}}|publisher = 哔哩哔哩弹幕网|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201218140856/https://space.bilibili.com/686127/|archive-date = 2020-12-18|dead-url = no}}</ref>。[[Herobrine|Herobrine]]是《我的世界》社区裡一個著名的[[都市傳說|都市傳說]]，首次出现在[[4chan|4chan]]的/v/版面中。据传闻，Herobrine会出现在玩家的世界中，并建造奇怪的建筑<ref name="ign">{{cite web|last=Dean|first=Paul|title=Hauntings and Hoaxes: Gamings Weirdest Ghost Stories|url=http://www.ign.com/articles/2011/10/31/hauntings-and-hoaxes-gamings-weirdest-ghost-stories|work=IGN|accessdate=2013-07-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160930145226/http://www.ign.com/articles/2011/10/31/hauntings-and-hoaxes-gamings-weirdest-ghost-stories|archive-date=2016-09-30|dead-url=no}}</ref>。然而，Mojang已确认Herobrine从未存在于《我的世界》，并且没有增加Herobrine的计划<ref name="dinnerbone-herobrine">{{cite web|url=https://twitter.com/dinnerbone/status/238278012632707072|title=Dinnerbone: @Kizzycocoa We have no plans ...|last=Adams|first=Nathan|date=2012-08-22|publisher=Twitter|accessdate=2013-07-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131107023431/https://twitter.com/dinnerbone/status/238278012632707072|archive-date=2013-11-07|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

《我的世界》被引用到许多其他游戏中，例如《[[RuneScape|RuneScape]]》、《[[火炬之光II|火炬之光II]]》、《[[无主之地2|无主之地2]]》、《[[直升机救人HD|直升机救人HD]]》、《[[超级肉食男孩|超级肉食男孩]]》、《[[上古卷轴V：天际|上古卷轴V：天际]]》、《[[以撒的结合|以撒的结合]]》、《[[軍團要塞2|军团要塞2]]》和《{{Le|FTL：超越光速|FTL: Faster Than Light}}》等<ref>{{cite web|last=Dean|first=Paul|title=Creeping up on you: The best Minecraft references in video games|url=http://www.pcgamesn.com/minecraft/creeping-you-best-minecraft-references-video-games|work=PCGamesN|publisher=Network N|accessdate=2012-11-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121101121747/http://www.pcgamesn.com/minecraft/creeping-you-best-minecraft-references-video-games|archive-date=2012-11-01|dead-url=no}}</ref>。游戏也被音乐家deadmau5在表演中引用<ref>{{cite web|last=Kennedy|first=Sam|title=Deadmau5 References Minecraft in New Show|url=http://www.ign.com/articles/2011/08/11/deadmau5-references-minecraft-in-new-show|work=[[IGN|IGN]]|accessdate=2012-11-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121110181644/http://www.ign.com/articles/2011/08/11/deadmau5-references-minecraft-in-new-show|archive-date=2012-11-10|dead-url=no}}</ref>。在美国歌手[[Lady_Gaga|Lady Gaga]]的单曲《[[男子漢_(歌曲)|男子汉]]》的MV中，出现了电脑运行《我的世界》的模拟画面，还可看到一条游戏指令<code>/gamemode [[ARTPOP|ARTPOP]]</code><ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=PNu_-deVemE |title=Lady Gaga – G.U.Y. - An ARTPOP Film – YouTube |publisher=YouTube.com |date=2014-03-22 |accessdate=2014-07-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140706002852/http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=PNu_-deVemE |archive-date=2014-07-06 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。在《我的世界》发布后，一些与其风格相似的游戏发布，有的甚至被称为游戏的“克隆”。在《我的世界》流行后，各种游戏平台都有许多类《我的世界》和受《我的世界》启发的游戏。如《[[黑桃A_(遊戲)|黑桃A]]》、《{{Le|CastleMiner|CastleMiner}}》、《{{Le|CraftWorld|CraftWorld}}》、《{{Le|FortressCraft|FortressCraft}}》、《[[泰拉瑞亚|泰拉瑞亚]]》和《{{Le|Total Miner|Total Miner}}》<ref>{{cite web|last=Webster|first=Andrew|title=Living under a blocky shadow: the world of Minecraft clones|url=http://arstechnica.com/gaming/2011/07/living-under-a-blocky-shadow-the-world-of-minecraft-clones/|work=[[Ars_Technica|Ars Technica]]|accessdate=2012-10-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131129001831/http://arstechnica.com/gaming/2011/07/living-under-a-blocky-shadow-the-world-of-minecraft-clones/|archive-date=2013-11-29|dead-url=no}}</ref>。《{{Le|The Blockheads|The Blockheads}}》的设计者大卫·弗兰普顿（David Frampton）称他的2D游戏失败的原因之一是“低分辨率像素艺术”与《我的世界》太相似导致在粉丝中产生“一些阻力”<ref name="FramptonPostMort">{{cite web |author=Frampton, David |title=Postmortem: The Blockheads |date=2013-10-12 |publisher=[[Gamasutra|Gamasutra]] |url=http://www.gamasutra.com/blogs/DavidFrampton/20131012/202246/Postmortem_The_Blockheads.php |access-date=2015-11-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150402124102/http://www.gamasutra.com/blogs/DavidFrampton/20131012/202246/Postmortem_The_Blockheads.php |archive-date=2015-04-02 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2020年10月1日，《[[任天堂明星大亂鬥_特別版|任天堂明星大亂鬥 特別版]]》宣布《我的世界》的主角史蒂夫和艾莉克斯作为新的可操控角色将加入到游戏中。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Minecraft is coming to Super Smash Bros. Ultimate|url=https://www.polygon.com/2020/10/1/21496832/super-smash-bros-ultimate-minecraft-dlc-fighter|accessdate=2020-10-02|work=www.polygon.com|language=en|archive-date=2021-01-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210111011122/https://www.polygon.com/2020/10/1/21496832/super-smash-bros-ultimate-minecraft-dlc-fighter|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=《任天堂明星大乱斗》新角色公布 来自《我的世界》史蒂夫_3DM单机|url=https://m.3dmgame.com/news/202010/3798783.html|accessdate=2020-10-02|work=m.3dmgame.com|archive-date=2020-10-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201002193736/https://m.3dmgame.com/news/202010/3798783.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=Minecraft's Steve Revealed As Super Smash Bros. Ultimate's Next DLC Fighter|url=https://www.nintendolife.com/news/2020/10/minecrafts_steve_revealed_as_super_smash_bros_ultimates_next_dlc_fighter|accessdate=2020-10-02|date=2020-10-01|last=Life|first=Nintendo|work=Nintendo Life|language=en-GB|archive-date=2021-01-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210113091646/https://www.nintendolife.com/news/2020/10/minecrafts_steve_revealed_as_super_smash_bros_ultimates_next_dlc_fighter|dead-url=no}}</ref>

=== 类似游戏 ===
此外，为了应对微软收购Mojang和《我的世界》的IP，众多开发商突然宣布正在于[[任天堂|任天堂]]游戏机上进一步开发其複製游戏，因为他们没有正式收到《我的世界》唯一主要平台的消息，虽然早期传言称本作将开发[[Wii_U|Wii U]]版本<ref name="NLcitesMinecraftWiiURumours">{{cite web |first=Damien |last=McFerran |url=http://www.nintendolife.com/news/2013/12/rumour_minecraft_is_already_in_development_for_wii_u_gamepad_said_to_be_the_focus |title=Rumour: Minecraft Is Already In Development For Wii U, GamePad Said To Be The Focus |publisher=Nintendo Life |date=2013-12-24 |accessdate=2014-11-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141129014900/http://www.nintendolife.com/news/2013/12/rumour_minecraft_is_already_in_development_for_wii_u_gamepad_said_to_be_the_focus |archive-date=2014-11-29 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。这些複製游戏有些为Wii U开发，如《{{Le|UCraft|UCraft}}》<ref name="NLcitesUCraft">{{cite web |first=Thomas |last=Whitehead |url=http://www.nintendolife.com/news/2014/09/nexis_games_is_developing_u_craft_a_minecraft_clone_for_the_eshop |title=Nexis Games is Developing U Craft, a Minecraft Clone, for the eShop |publisher=Nintendo Life |date=2014-09-30 |accessdate=2014-11-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141110150412/http://www.nintendolife.com/news/2014/09/nexis_games_is_developing_u_craft_a_minecraft_clone_for_the_eshop |archive-date=2014-11-10 |dead-url=no }}</ref>和《{{Le|方块世界：孤岛求生|Cube Life: Island Survival}}》<ref name="NLcitesCLIS">{{cite web |first=Darren |last=Calvert |url=http://www.nintendolife.com/news/2015/01/cube_life_island_survival_is_another_minecraft-inspired_title_heading_to_the_wii_u_eshop |title=Cube Life: Island Survival is Another Minecraft-Inspired Title Heading to the Wii U eShop |publisher=Nintendo Life |date=2015-01-19 |accessdate=2015-01-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150119235034/http://www.nintendolife.com/news/2015/01/cube_life_island_survival_is_another_minecraft-inspired_title_heading_to_the_wii_u_eshop |archive-date=2015-01-19 |dead-url=no }}</ref>；有些为[[任天堂3DS|任天堂3DS]]开发，如《Battleminer》<ref name="NLcitesBattleminer">{{cite web |first=Thomas |last=Whitehead |url=http://www.nintendolife.com/news/2014/09/battleminer_screens_show_some_familiar_block_building_on_the_way_to_3ds |title=Battleminer Screens Show Some Familiar Block Building On the Way to 3DS |publisher=Nintendo Life |date=2014-10-01 |accessdate=2014-11-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141102094010/http://www.nintendolife.com/news/2014/09/battleminer_screens_show_some_familiar_block_building_on_the_way_to_3ds |archive-date=2014-11-02 |dead-url=no }}</ref>和《Cube Creator 3D》<ref name="NLcitesCubeCreator3D">{{cite web |first=Darren |last=Calvert |url=http://www.nintendolife.com/news/2014/10/another_minecraft_clone_cube_creator_3d_coming_to_3ds_eshop |title=Another Minecraft Clone, Cube Creator 3D Coming To 3DS eShop |publisher=Nintendo Life |date=2014-10-31 |accessdate=2014-11-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141102141601/http://www.nintendolife.com/news/2014/10/another_minecraft_clone_cube_creator_3d_coming_to_3ds_eshop |archive-date=2014-11-02 |dead-url=no }}</ref>；或者同时支持Wii U和3DS，如《Stone Shire》<ref name="NLcitesStoneShire">{{cite web |first=Thomas |last=Whitehead |url=http://www.nintendolife.com/news/2014/10/more_minecraft_mania_looks_set_for_wii_u_with_stone_shire |title=More Minecraft Mania Looks Set for Wii U With Stone Shire |publisher=Nintendo Life |date=2014-10-01 |accessdate=2014-11-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141106014641/http://www.nintendolife.com/news/2014/10/more_minecraft_mania_looks_set_for_wii_u_with_stone_shire |archive-date=2014-11-06 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。在[[Kotaku|Kotaku]]对宫本茂与高桥伸也的采访中提到了《我的世界》登陆任天堂平台。宫本表示{{Le|Wii U游戏手柄|Wii U GamePad}}是游戏的一个“不错的选择”，并且任天堂可以在日本普及这款游戏<ref name="KotakuNintendoMinecraftInterview">{{cite web |first=Stephen |last=Totilo |url=http://kotaku.com/what-nintendos-top-game-creators-think-of-minecraft-1593839008 |title=What Nintendo's Top Game Creators Think Of Minecraft |work=[[Kotaku|Kotaku]] |date=2014-06-20 |accessdate=2014-11-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141129023510/http://kotaku.com/what-nintendos-top-game-creators-think-of-minecraft-1593839008 |archive-date=2014-11-29 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2015年7月，Mojang[[首席运营官|首席运营官]]Vu Bui在采访透露《我的世界》将登陆新的平台，包括任天堂主机，并宣称微软的收购不会妨碍这种前景。Bui表示“我们没有理由拒绝登陆Wii U或3DS，只不过还未提上日程。”<ref name="MCV-UK_interview">{{cite web |first=Alex |last=Calvin |url=http://www.mcvuk.com/news/read/mojang-s-block-party-what-is-next-for-minecraft/ |title=Mojang's block party - what is next for Minecraft? |publisher=MCV UK |date=2015-07-09 |accessdate=2015-07-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150712044341/http://www.mcvuk.com/news/read/mojang-s-block-party-what-is-next-for-minecraft/ |archive-date=2015-07-12 |dead-url=no }}</ref>2015年8月，Telltale Games确认番外作品《Minecraft：故事模式》将登陆Wii U，成为系列中第一款登陆任天堂主机的游戏<ref name="VergecitesMSMonWiiU">{{cite web |first=Andrew |last=Webster |url=http://www.theverge.com/2015/8/26/9207085/minecraft-story-mode-telltale-games-interview |title=Giving Minecraft a story |work=[[The_Verge|The Verge]] |date=2015-08-26 |accessdate=2015-08-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150827005650/http://www.theverge.com/2015/8/26/9207085/minecraft-story-mode-telltale-games-interview |archive-date=2015-08-27 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

=== 改编 ===
2012年，Mojang收到了好莱坞制作人的交易请求，他们想制作《我的世界》相关的电视节目。不过，Mojang表示他们将在“正确的想法出现时”从事此类项目<ref name="Merchandise sales" />。2012年12月，由[[2_Player_Productions|2 Player Productions]]制作的有关Mojang和《我的世界》发展历程的纪录片《[[當個創世神：Mojang的故事|Minecraft：Mojang的故事]]》发行<ref>{{cite web | url=http://kotaku.com/5970346/minecraft-the-story-of-mojang-the-kotaku-review | title=Minecraft: The Story of Mojang: The Kotaku Review | work=[[Kotaku|Kotaku]] | publisher=Gawker Media | date=2012-12-21 | accessdate=2013-01-03 | last=Hawkins | first=Matt | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121230181901/http://kotaku.com/5970346/minecraft-the-story-of-mojang-the-kotaku-review | archive-date=2012-12-30 | dead-url=no }}</ref>。在动画连续剧《[[南方公園|南方四賤客]]》第十七季的的第二集“Informative Murder Porn”中，男孩用《我的世界》分散其父母的注意力防止他们争吵<ref>{{cite web |last=Schreier |first=Jason |url=http://kotaku.com/this-weeks-south-park-is-all-about-minecraft-1427305010 |title=This Week's South Park Is All About ''Minecraft'' |date=2013-09-30 |accessdate=2013-10-01 |work=Kotaku |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130930203114/http://kotaku.com/this-weeks-south-park-is-all-about-minecraft-1427305010 |archive-date=2013-09-30 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。在剧集中，脾气暴躁科里·兰思金（Corey Lanskin）解释道，“Minecraft里没有赢家，也没有目标，你只管他妈的胡建乱造。”<ref>{{cite web |first=Max |last=Nicholson |date=2013-10-03 |title=Minecraft for dummies |work=[[IGN|IGN]] |url=http://www.ign.com/articles/2013/10/03/south-park-informative-murder-porn-review |accessdate=2013-12-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131028023600/http://www.ign.com/articles/2013/10/03/south-park-informative-murder-porn-review |archive-date=2013-10-28 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

2014年2月27日，Notch透露Mojang正在与[[华纳兄弟|华纳兄弟]]展开合作，将《我的世界》搬上大银幕，并由《[[樂高玩電影|樂高玩電影]]》制片人罗伊·李（Roy Lee）和吉尔·梅西克（Jill Messick）联合打造<ref>{{cite web|title=Minecraft movie in the works with Warner Bros.|url=http://www.gamasutra.com/view/news/211920/Minecraft_movie_in_the_works_with_Warner_Bros.php|accessdate=2014-02-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140228080450/http://gamasutra.com/view/news/211920/Minecraft_movie_in_the_works_with_Warner_Bros.php|archive-date=2014-02-28|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |last=Busch |first=Anita |title=Video Game Sensation 'Minecraft' Coming To The Big Screen As Warner Bros Acquires Rights; 'Lego's' Roy Lee And Jill Messick Producing |url=http://www.deadline.com/2014/02/minecraft-movie-warner-bros-lego-movie-producer/ |publisher=Deadline |date=2014-02-27 |accessdate=2014-02-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140228170036/http://www.deadline.com/2014/02/minecraft-movie-warner-bros-lego-movie-producer/ |archive-date=2014-02-28 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2014年10月8日，Mojang[[首席运营官|首席运营官]]Vu Bui表示电影尚处于“早期制作阶段”，并称这是一个“大预算”电影，可能会于2018年发行<ref>{{cite web|title=Minecraft Movie Is "Large-Budget," Might Not Arrive Until 2018|url=http://www.gamespot.com/articles/minecraft-movie-is-large-budget-might-not-arrive-u/1100-6422821/|publisher=GameSpot|accessdate=2014-10-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141010053324/http://www.gamespot.com/articles/minecraft-movie-is-large-budget-might-not-arrive-u/1100-6422821/|archive-date=2014-10-10|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Minecraft movie will be 'large-budget' but unlikely to arrive before 2017|url=http://www.theguardian.com/technology/2014/oct/08/minecraft-movies-youtube-mojang-licensing?view=desktop/|work=The Guardian|accessdate=2014-10-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141021054937/http://www.theguardian.com/technology/2014/oct/08/minecraft-movies-youtube-mojang-licensing?view=desktop%2F|archive-date=2014-10-21|dead-url=no}}</ref>。电影原定于2019年5月24日上映，由[[肖恩·利维|肖恩·利维]]执导，贾森·福克斯编剧<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/heat-vision/warner-bros-minecraft-movie-gets-906607|title=Warner Bros.' 'Minecraft' Movie Gets Release Date|publisher=The Hollywood Reporter|last=Galuppo|first=Mia|date=2016-06-27|access-date=2016-12-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160628141028/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/heat-vision/warner-bros-minecraft-movie-gets-906607|archive-date=2016-06-28|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|last1=Kroll|first1=Justin|title=Warner Bros. Taps Shawn Levy for 'Minecraft' Movie|url=http://variety.com/2014/film/news/warner-bros-taps-shawn-levy-for-minecraft-movie-1201332000/|accessdate=2014-10-16|work=Variety|date=2014-10-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141017174929/http://variety.com/2014/film/news/warner-bros-taps-shawn-levy-for-minecraft-movie-1201332000/|archive-date=2014-10-17|dead-url=no}}</ref>。利維後來離開了導演職位，由[[羅布·麥克亨尼|羅布·麥克亨尼]]接手<ref>{{cite web|url=http://deadline.com/2015/07/minecraft-movie-rob-mcelhenney-its-always-sunny-in-philadelphia-1201482930/|title=Minecraft Movie Gets 'It's Always Sunny In Philadelphia's Rob McElhenney|publisher=Deadline|last=Fleming, Jr|first=Mike|date=2015-07-21|access-date=2015-11-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150722190910/http://deadline.com/2015/07/minecraft-movie-rob-mcelhenney-its-always-sunny-in-philadelphia-1201482930/|archive-date=2015-07-22|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://variety.com/2016/film/news/jason-fuchs-minecraft-movie-writer-1201888253/ |title=‘Wonder Woman’ Scribe Jason Fuchs to Write Latest Draft of ‘Minecraft’ (EXCLUSIVE) |publisher=Variety |last=Kroll |first=Justin |date=2016-10-13 |access-date=2016-12-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161017174723/http://variety.com/2016/film/news/jason-fuchs-minecraft-movie-writer-1201888253/ |archive-date=2016-10-17 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2018年8月，麥克亨尼退出了劇組，福克斯被兄弟檔編劇{{link-en|尼兄弟|Aaron and Adam Nee|亞倫·尼與亞當·尼}}取代，上映日期因此延後<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.thewrap.com/minecraft-nee-brothers-rob-mcelhenny-release-date/|title='Minecraft' Movie Delayed: Rob McElhenney Out as Director, Nee Brothers Tapped to Write (Exclusive)|website=The Wrap|last1=Gonzalez|first1=Umberto|last2=Maglio|first2=Tony|date=2018-08-03|accessdate=2018-08-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180804031124/https://www.thewrap.com/minecraft-nee-brothers-rob-mcelhenny-release-date/|archive-date=2018-08-04|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2019年1月，據報導，{{link-en|彼得·蘇列特|Peter Sollett}}將身兼該片的導演和編劇<ref>{{cite web|url=https://variety.com/2019/film/news/peter-sollett-warner-bros-minecraft-1203105640/|title=Peter Sollett to Direct Warner Bros.' 'Minecraft' Movie (EXCLUSIVE)|website=[[Variety_(magazine)|Variety]]|last=Kroll|first=Justin|date=2019-01-11|access-date=2019-01-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190112061341/https://variety.com/2019/film/news/peter-sollett-warner-bros-minecraft-1203105640/|archive-date=2019-01-12|dead-url=no}}</ref>。据2019年4月的報導，該片預計於2022年3月4日在美國院-{zh-hant:線上;zh-hans:线上}-映<ref>{{Cite web|title=THE MINECRAFT MOVIE IS JUST AROUND THE CORNER|url=https://www.minecraft.net/zh-hans/article/the-minecraft-movie-is-just-around-the-corner|accessdate=2020-01-01|date=2019-04-16|work=Minecraft.net|language=zh-CN|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200101025639/https://www.minecraft.net/zh-hans/article/the-minecraft-movie-is-just-around-the-corner|archive-date=2020-01-01|dead-url=no}}</ref>。后因COVID-19疫情于2020年10月5日再次宣布推迟，具体发行日未知。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/heat-vision/the-batman-delays-release-to-2022-as-warner-bros-shuffles-calendar|title=‘The Batman’ Delays Release to 2022 as Warner Bros. Shuffles Calendar|website=The Hollywood Reporter|date=2020-10-5|access-date=2021-07-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210724131302/https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/movies/movie-news/the-batman-delays-release-to-2022-as-warner-bros-shuffles-calendar-4071618/|archive-date=2021-07-24|dead-url=no}}</ref>

=== 商品 ===

{{See also|樂高版我的世界}}

以[[樂高|乐高积木]]为原型的《乐高版Minecraft》于2012年6月6日发布<ref>{{cite web|url=http://news.yahoo.com/blogs/technology-blog/lego-releases-minecraft-set-ve-waiting-160151420.html|title=Lego releases the Minecraft set you've been waiting for|work=Yahoo! News|publisher=[[雅虎|Yahoo!]]|first=Mariella|last=Moon|date=2012-06-06|access-date=2015-10-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120609004319/http://news.yahoo.com/blogs/technology-blog/lego-releases-minecraft-set-ve-waiting-160151420.html|archive-date=2012-06-09|dead-url=no}}</ref>。游戏世界称为“Micro World”，以[[玩家角色|玩家角色]]和苦力怕为中心<ref name="LegoMinecraft">{{cite web | last = MacManus | first = Christopher | url = http://news.cnet.com/8301-17938_105-57379791-1/lego-minecraft-available-for-preorder/ | title = Lego Minecraft available for preorder | date = 2012-02-16 | accessdate = 2012-02-17 | work = [[CNET|CNET]] | publisher = [[CBS互動|CBS Interactive]] | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20120217114653/http://news.cnet.com/8301-17938_105-57379791-1/lego-minecraft-available-for-preorder/ | archive-date = 2012-02-17 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。Mojang于2011年11月向乐高提交了《我的世界》商品的概念并在Lego Cuusoo网站发布。它的票数很快达到了一万，从而促使乐高关注这一概念<ref name="LEGO">{{cite web|url=http://kotaku.com/5878848/there-will-be-official-minecraft-lego-sets|title=There Will Be Official Minecraft Lego Sets|work=[[Kotaku|Kotaku]]|publisher=Gawker Media|first=Stephen|last=Totilo|date=2012-01-24|access-date=2015-10-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120606064402/http://kotaku.com/5878848/there-will-be-official-minecraft-lego-sets|archive-date=2012-06-06|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2012年1月，《我的世界》概念被Lego Cuusoo批准并开始开发<ref name="LEGO" />。2013年9月1日，基于下界和乡村设定的游戏发布。2014年6月，第四个设定“末地”发布。11月，有6个游戏设定发布<ref>{{cite web|author1=LEGO|title=LEGO Minecraft|url=https://www.facebook.com/LEGOMinecraft/photos/a.299460193452063.72516.250707394994010/778262168905194/?type=1|website=Facebook.com|publisher=Facebook|accessdate=2014-10-05|date=2014-09-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151106171607/https://www.facebook.com/LEGOMinecraft/photos/a.299460193452063.72516.250707394994010/778262168905194/?type=1|archive-date=2015-11-06|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

Mojang和网上游戏商品店Jinx合作，销售衣服、泡沫镐、[[苦力帕|苦力帕]]玩偶以及其他於遊戲中出现的动物玩具等《我的世界》商品<ref name="Cult and merchandise">{{cite web | url=http://www.wired.co.uk/magazine/archive/2012/07/features/changing-the-game?page=all | title=Changing the game: how Notch made Minecraft a cult hit | work=Wired UK | date=2012-06-06 | accessdate=2012-10-18 | last=Cheshire | first=Tom | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121124095359/http://www.wired.co.uk/magazine/archive/2012/07/features/changing-the-game?page=all | archive-date=2012-11-24 | dead-url=no }}</ref>。截至2012年5月，《我的世界》商品销售额超过100万美元。T恤和袜子是最热门的产品<ref name="Merchandise sales">{{cite web|last=Nunneley|first=Stephany|title=Minecraft hits $80M in sales with over 5M paid downloads|url=http://www.vg247.com/2012/03/24/minecraft-hits-80m-in-sales-with-over-5m-paid-downloads/|work=[[VG247|VG247]]|date=2012-03-24|accessdate=2012-11-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120326175441/http://www.vg247.com/2012/03/24/minecraft-hits-80m-in-sales-with-over-5m-paid-downloads/|archive-date=2012-03-26|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2013年3月，Mojang与儿童图书出版商{{Le|Egmont Group|Egmont Group}}签署协议，打造《我的世界》手册、年鉴、海报书籍和杂志<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.polygon.com/2013/3/26/4148622/minecraft-books-for-children-to-be-published-in-uk-this-september|title=Minecraft books for children to be published in UK this September|work=[[Polygon|Polygon]]|accessdate=2013-03-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130329141714/http://www.polygon.com/2013/3/26/4148622/minecraft-books-for-children-to-be-published-in-uk-this-september|archive-date=2013-03-29|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.develop-online.net/news/43618/Minecraft-childrens-books-launching-in-September | title=Minecraft children's books launching in September | work=[[開發者_(雜誌)|Develop]] | date=2013-03-25 | accessdate=2013-03-28 | author=Chapple, Craig | deadurl=yes | archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130328105927/http://www.develop-online.net/news/43618/Minecraft-childrens-books-launching-in-September | archivedate=2013-03-28 }}</ref><ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.wired.co.uk/news/archive/2013-03/27/minecraft-books | title=Gaming Minecraft children's books announced | publisher=Wired.com | date=2013-03-27 | accessdate=2013-03-28 | author=Warr, Philippa | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160305002510/http://www.wired.co.uk/news/archive/2013-03/27/minecraft-books | archive-date=2016-03-05 | dead-url=no }}</ref>。{{le|Scholastic|Scholastic Corporation}}发售了《我的世界》必备手册。2017年7月10日，网易《我的世界》官方周边商城正式上线运行<ref>{{cite web|url=http://mc.163.com/news/2017/07/10/25510_699434.html|title=《我的世界》官方周边商城上线啦！_我的世界Minecraft中国版官方网站——你想玩的，这里都有|website=mc.163.com|access-date=2017-07-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170713111739/http://mc.163.com/news/2017/07/10/25510_699434.html|archive-date=2017-07-13|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

=== Minecon ===
{{Main|MineCon}}

[[MineCon|MineCon]]是由Mojang官方举办的《我的世界》爱好者聚会。2011年11月18日-19日，第一次聚会在[[曼德勒海灣度假村|曼德勒海湾度假村]]酒店和[[内华达州|内华达州]][[拉斯维加斯|拉斯维加斯]]的赌场中举行。为2011年MineCon准备的所有4500张门票在10月31日售罄<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.kotaku.com.au/2011/10/well-whaddaya-know-minecon-is-sold-out/|title=Well Whaddaya Know: MineCon Is Sold Out|work=[[Kotaku|Kotaku]]|publisher=Gawker Media|first=Owen|last=Good|date=2012-10-31|accessdate=2013-01-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130203113607/http://www.kotaku.com.au/2011/10/well-whaddaya-know-minecon-is-sold-out/|archive-date=2013-02-03|dead-url=no}}</ref>。本次活动包括推出《我的世界》新版、主题演讲、建筑和服装比赛、《我的世界》主题讨论组、官方及相关公司展览、纪念商品以及与Mojang员工和《我的世界》社区知名贡献者进行签名及合影<ref>{{cite web |url=http://uk.pc.gamespy.com/pc/minecraft/1187399p1.html |title=GameSpy: Tickets for Minecraft Convention, MineCon, Now On Sale —Page 1 |work=[[GameSpy|GameSpy]] |publisher=Glu Mobile |date=2011-08-11 |accessdate=2011-12-18 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6Ed6ETSPG?url=http://uk.pc.gamespy.com/pc/minecraft/1187399p1.html |archivedate=2013-02-22 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。在MineCon结束后，人们还会与电子音乐家[[鼠來寶_(DJ)|电子鼠]]进行“进入下界”（Into The Nether）活动<ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.ign.com/articles/2011/11/22/deadmau5-blows-the-roof-off-of-minecon | title=Into the Nether party with deadmau5 | work=[[IGN|IGN]] | date=2011-11-22 | accessdate=2012-09-25 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121106094628/http://www.ign.com/articles/2011/11/22/deadmau5-blows-the-roof-off-of-minecon | archive-date=2012-11-06 | dead-url=no }}</ref>。每位参加聚会的玩家会免费获得由Mojang开发的另一款游戏《{{Le|Scrolls|Scrolls (video game)}}》和Oxeye Game Studios开发的《[[Cobalt_(游戏)|Cobalt]]》游戏的内测资格<ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.joystiq.com/2011/09/08/minecon-attendees-get-alpha-codes-for-cobalt-scrolls/ | title=MineCon attendees get alpha codes for Cobalt, Scrolls | work=[[Joystiq|Joystiq]] | publisher=[[美国在线|AOL]] | date=2011-09-08 | accessdate=2012-11-23 | first=Griffin | last=McElroy | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130616022327/http://www.joystiq.com/2011/09/08/minecon-attendees-get-alpha-codes-for-cobalt-scrolls/ | archive-date=2013-06-16 | dead-url=yes }}</ref>。2012年11月，聚会在[[巴黎迪士尼樂園度假區|巴黎迪士尼乐园度假区]]举行<ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/technology-20492574 | title=Minecraft fans gather for Minecon in Paris | work=[[英國廣播公司新聞網|BBC News Online]] | publisher=BBC | date=2012-11-26 | accessdate=2012-12-23 | last=Ward | first=Mark | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130111022225/http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/technology-20492574 | archive-date=2013-01-11 | dead-url=no }}</ref>。其门票在不到两小时内售罄<ref>{{cite web|last=Corriera|first=Alexa Ray|work=[[Polygon|Polygon]]|publisher=Vox Media|title=Minecon 2012 tickets sell out in two hours, Mojang looking into releasing more|url=http://www.polygon.com/gaming/2012/9/14/3332678/minecon-2012-ticket-sell-out|date=2012-09-14|accessdate=2012-12-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130328203220/http://www.polygon.com/gaming/2012/9/14/3332678/minecon-2012-ticket-sell-out|archive-date=2013-03-28|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2013年11月，聚会在美国[[佛罗里达州|佛罗里达州]][[奥兰多_(佛罗里达州)|奥兰多]]举行<ref>{{cite web|last=Winters|first=Lydia|url=https://twitter.com/LydiaWinters/status/320922859411230720|title=MINECON will be in the US this year. Sorry dear Brits. I'm not coming to scout locations!|publisher=Twitter|date=2013-04-07|accessdate=2013-06-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131026014537/https://twitter.com/LydiaWinters/status/320922859411230720|archive-date=2013-10-26|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=lNG_Ayqb-ts|title=Where in the World is MINECON 2013?|publisher=YouTube|date=2013-06-27|accessdate=2013-06-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130813032054/http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=lNG_Ayqb-ts|archive-date=2013-08-13|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2015年7月，聚会在英国伦敦举行<ref>{{cite web|url=https://mojang.com/2014/08/minecon-2015/|title=MINECON 2015|publisher=Mojang AB|date=2014-08-21|accessdate=2014-09-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/2014